'''阿片样肽受体'''或'''阿片类受体'''、'''阿片受体'''（{{lang-en|Opioid receptors}}）是一类以[[阿片样肽|阿片样肽]]为[[配体_(生物化学)|配体]]的[[G蛋白偶联受体|G蛋白偶联受体]]<ref name="pmid8981566">{{cite journal | author = Dhawan BN, Cesselin F, Raghubir R, Reisine T, Bradley PB, Portoghese PS, Hamon M | title = International Union of Pharmacology. XII. Classification of opioid receptors | journal = Pharmacol. Rev. | volume = 48 | issue = 4 | pages = 567–92 | pmid = 8981566 | doi = | url = | issn = |date=December 1996}}</ref><ref name="pmid14754373">{{cite journal | author = Janecka A, Fichna J, Janecki T | title = Opioid receptors and their ligands | journal = Curr Top Med Chem | volume = 4 | issue = 1 | pages = 1–17 | year = 2004 | pmid = 14754373 | doi = | url = | issn = }}</ref><ref name="pmid15189164">{{cite journal | author = Waldhoer M, Bartlett SE, Whistler JL | title = Opioid receptors | journal = Annu. Rev. Biochem. | volume = 73 | issue = | pages = 953–90 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15189164 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.biochem.73.011303.073940 | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_annual-review-of-biochemistry_2004_73/page/953| issn = }}</ref>。[[内源性|内源性]]类阿片物质包括[[强啡肽|强啡肽]]、{{le|脑啡肽|enkephalin}}、[[内啡肽|内啡肽]]、{{tsl|en|endomorphin||endomorphin}}和{{tsl|en|nociceptin||nociceptin}}。 阿片样肽受体与[[生长抑素|生长抑素]][[受体_(生物化学)|受体]]（SSTRs）有约40%的相似性。阿片受体广泛分布于[[大脑|大脑]]，且在[[脊髓|脊髓]]与[[消化道|消化道]]中也有发现。

